<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Please do not confuse Lamentation with the Lamentation Blade. They are two completely different weapons. The first is a 1 hander dropped in Kunark and 2nd is a 2 hander dropped in Kedge Keep. They are two very different very, real weapons. I have seen them both.</font></td></tr></table>
