<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: ranger of darkness</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-09-15 02:47:00</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>First of all this item is a rare of sebilite guardian, the common is the Larrikans mask, and i believe Jaundiced arms, and the Wind Saber(ranger bow)are the super rare drops.  This item is best primary 1HS in game, plus adds some nice stats.  The camp is really easy to run there are no trains and rarely get more than 2 at a time.  The perfect group for this camp is Ranger Shaman Cleric Warrior Chanter and Mage for the air pet's stunning ability.  Ranger pulls secondary(mob to be mezzed) with snare and primary runs directly(mob to be killed first) after puller and is assisted upon by warrior.  <BR>
<BR>
Uber ranger</font></td></tr></table>
